@startuml
title UC02 — User registers/logs in/resets password/OAuth Google — State Diagram
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> InProgress : submit authentication request
InProgress --> Validating : submit/request
Validating --> Completed : success
Validating --> Error : validation/integration/access error
Error --> InProgress : retry/fix input
Completed --> [*]
state Completed {
  [*] --> ResultVisible
  ResultVisible --> Saved : User updated/read
  Saved --> [*]
}
@enduml
